on the first day of his tour of yugoslavia, which has its own nationality problems, the soviet communist party chief was asked about recent demonstrations and ethnic riots in southern soviet republics
show me the country in which there are no such problems,'' he replied. ``if you show me, i will travel there right away, without stopping in moscow on return from yugoslavia.''
